;W[rs]LB[ss:1][ps:2][rs:3]C[Dia. 01 Correct Answer

{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}

White's placement at the \cf1\b 1-1 point\cf0\b0  is the only way to capture Black.

This move is rarely used, but it can be a powerful vital point

After Black 2, White destroys the eye with 3 and Black doesn't have enough space to live.
