;B[ss]LB[ps:1][qs:2][os:3][ss:4]C[Dia. 04 Bad Exchange


White 1 is the move what Black was hoping for.

After Black takes at 2, it becomes miai. If White plays at 3, Black makes two eyes with 4. If White plays at 4 instead of 3, Black plays at 3 and lives again.

It means White 1 is a bad exchange.


])
